fying Scala issues**\\n\\nI need to find a fix and consider removing `scala3-compiler` from compileOnly. The Gradle Scala plugin might require scalaClasspath, but it actually passed, which is interesting. There might be an issue with the Scala 3 compiler or library, particularly around `scala.runtime.LazyVals` lambdas. The error about \\\"Enclosing method not found\\\" pops up when calling getGenericSuperclass on hidden lambda classes. I believe there's a GraalVM bug affecting reflection registration, so I need to ensure no hidden lambda classes are in the image heap.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_01dabda23fd64c9e016a23a0c05558819097756746aa3c2d6c\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"content\\\":[],\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABqI6DQVj6fai3zHi8EL218d7o-uoHwqm7n9O2yStpI3MuuBIcxCrR8MKASohwaIXZT0_OV-eTYoEUx0uzGwaIIbDTq08oqzBO5sdLEv4TgA_lsuBwkCh67NPc1iCdtGrIld1WHZ4QL8sa9zJ_4IXOlehfo_8INmH24Gsz2jeHwxMK18IlKSrnhaYCQdS09-NovM5sU8cZxf4PodoZepMzjwljUTlr37aHhzknOpHCnaQedYWYd6IO44DwaToMmxKCnw3OILWfM1xk_P_tHogD0Hr6WSxMGa0gBlUiOw3pSxJ_6RyQvVfqJjnIp6PXIUANuhqZr19SLO9aT4eObKl_WXn9-NbMywTh7-69BLYyTyJDWX_7uZzYp4hOzT9kHH_GQ7NnNxjLh0TE-bmwyVZH_jhC4LJliVmjiSnlLlarpMjavOeIB-669u9w7SOMt7X_pXkiRZUhvzvsbqM_f_nTAU5zmp1pfnOqYLuPk9jtFFnUz4b-q3moHH9ogwWcEKvpyIsrSSeWnqlOCU7Icgcy9jaC92KfDOJNP7-uv1i21s5-P-_16J1DO-xEXdpuAo2oEJDOsLvBkRE_r6W1GgLyeDfH1l2WBliIzQZPZIOBY9HNxwZB9QA271Ul3XssOkhte55v9_PV4QlZoFdmBZzfuFVhUb62MBqjfhkhed7chUIJ2vpsuytQlm4-sC9yEUP2oJvlo00pys8ORA81htbP7lmj2LwdaTwX1xR5oMwxpDDH6dhbK2J4_vhGW94DABVyzcSOxo63MsK8VNr0CTeNOyfcPD9-_X5Cvozsdy5A1UMQPo-ILmU62dLjhfrVe0CWBlD1EQzRJsO3D6vLFvV_tjzCmGmGVNo0FBuC-NF6V8W2eXnIWeCOrUMU1ppDijl-PGvbvnpeZPpqf9BPGvc03VbldPY7rudt0anaZC5MijUvb0UatPvx36UXSopon4i9uMq-Ng1gQU6kTnidTrFAgfjBA4Sbj4T13DkCkGZJnY9xLBVkmi1GY4peqpqdvQfTGQWOexbioOYjYiDP57nKHGaBYDCxl61xmBGrk0maPNGPSYUPTLfd6Hn-nKGiOgVQnuIThFcWzlFtfJrZ5sW-xy0Au99dbdXYvIddeq3itosFMndiF7pNYxWHH6cpC9Cns-wUV2NJgtZu8kDB-FsT9DFmAXeEALl2Z2BKai_aJEmzV5AGRUSioPmDyXXbLBFGlvy3Iwd7G2CpBzx8_GkD